				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/matt/27.29?lang=eng#28" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Matt. 27:29</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/mark/15.17?lang=eng#16" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Mark 15:17</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/john/19.2,5?lang=eng#1" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">John 19:2, 5</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-96911_000_015"><a name="-96911_000_015">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote36-96911_000_015">36.</a>
      </span>
				<p><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/9.16?lang=eng#15" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">3 Ne. 9:16</a>; see also <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/6.21?lang=eng#20" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 6:21</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/10.57?lang=eng#56" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 10:57</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/11.29?lang=eng#28" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 11:29</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.3?lang=eng#2" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 39:3</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.8?lang=eng#7" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 45:8</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.66?lang=eng#65" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 133:66</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-96911_000_015"><a name="-96911_000_015">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote37-96911_000_015">37.</a>
      </span>
				<p><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/john/19.28?lang=eng#27" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">John 19:28</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-96911_000_015"><a name="-96911_000_015">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote38-96911_000_015">38.</a>
      </span>
				<p><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/mark/14.36?lang=eng#35" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Mark 14:36</a>. The word <span class="emphasis">Abba</span> is significant. <span class="emphasis">Ab</span> means &ldquo;father&rdquo;; <span class="emphasis">Abba</span> is an endearing and tender form of that term. The nearest English equivalent might be <span class="emphasis">Daddy.</span></p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-96911_000_015"><a name="-96911_000_015">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote39-96911_000_015">39.</a>
      </span>
				<p>Centuries later, the Lord shared innermost recollections of this experience with the Prophet Joseph Smith, the record of which we read in Doctrine and Covenants 19 [<a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/19.1-24?lang=eng#0" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 19:1&ndash;24</a>].</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-96911_000_015"><a name="-96911_000_015">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote40-96911_000_015">40.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/14.7?lang=eng#6" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 14:7</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-96911_000_015"><a name="-96911_000_015">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote41-96911_000_015">41.</a>
      </span>
				<p>Bruce R. McConkie, <span class="emphasis">The Promised Messiah</span> (1978), 568.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-96911_000_015"><a name="-96911_000_015">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote42-96911_000_015">42.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/2.3?lang=eng#2" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 2:3</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/138.48?lang=eng#47" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 138:48</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-96911_000_015"><a name="-96911_000_015">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote43-96911_000_015">43.</a>
      </span>
				<p><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/107.23?lang=eng#22" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 107:23</a>.</p>
			</li>
		</ol>
                                        
